{"tid":416391,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[經濟]點解香港工時相比歐洲咁長?","createTime":"2017-09-27T17:32:16.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-07T06:21:56.000Z","uid":70760,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"d10634268c4bc5317e7b6ae035e9c9cb0f30fd40","tid":416391,"uid":70760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T17:32:16.000Z","msg":"人地一般6小時一日左右, <br />\n<br />\n1.當中差異係咩原因? <br />\n<br />\n2.有咩阻力導致?<br />\n<br />\n3.假設克服左同歐洲一樣香港又會變成咩環境?<br />\n<br />\n求經濟學家share<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ed1e83ace3dc8209ceac18ccb46d9d45139d2be","tid":416391,"uid":29702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T17:35:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b659c11eb2116fd2059db59fb61981eb987c6391","tid":416391,"uid":53922,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T17:37:52.000Z","msg":"奴性重。"},{"pid":"527e70fb669fba2ed3f99861cce44404faeca58f","tid":416391,"uid":31773,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T17:38:51.000Z","msg":"人口密度間接影響所有商業需求<br />\n<br />\n同埋歐洲工時事實唔短<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n基本都係八個鐘一日，只不過少ot情況發生<br />\n<br />\n更重要係假期多<br />\n<br />\n香港老勢壓榨到盡先會咁痴線"},{"pid":"c905e401b4a894b194dae461b33b8cea2b34fb13","tid":416391,"uid":39698,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T17:41:25.000Z","msg":"因為人地D打工仔齊心囉，福利唔夠罷工，人工唔夠罷工...仲要罷得黎係團結咁罷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n相反香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"197b884a02eedd663298e2ed257501b2ce2f871f","tid":416391,"uid":29702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T17:44:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"16ecfe8968392cc6c6ea64e6ef6f07f0ced1e546","tid":416391,"uid":100760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T17:50:12.000Z","msg":"歐洲人使唔使煩買樓？真心唔知"},{"pid":"95427bdb75d2bed