 />\n<br />\n香港老勢壓榨到盡先會咁痴線</blockquote><br />\n點睇法國一星期返 36 小時？"},{"pid":"f2a11fe2a35b072dfca0019e7e92604dd3f71e13","tid":416391,"uid":67254,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T20:16:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你接唔接受到8點就成條街冇野買先？</blockquote><br />\n有咩咁難接受?"},{"pid":"5c2e724f99d7b863e82a096fcd7fb31c5c436fc5","tid":416391,"uid":48796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T02:06:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e80dd9c4ef44d4e8a8efe9795f0ec9aa44aa181","tid":416391,"uid":35192,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T02:19:10.000Z","msg":"所以咪有經濟危機囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06699f2e1b9123ef07e6c8fb4baed7ebbd88035b","tid":416391,"uid":14250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T02:22:21.000Z","msg":"做完就走得，你香港仲強制留人扮工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c4b12f26ca3c5febf3c19c413ed023d240e6a26","tid":416391,"uid":48796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T03:10:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>所以咪有經濟危機囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n買到樓未？"},{"pid":"e0b1089e990433e30493f7183444b64b936279e5","tid":416391,"uid":132302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T03:13:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你接唔接受到8點就成條街冇野買先？</blockquote><br />\n輪姦制如果排得好<br />\n其實都買到嘢㗎喎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d8274cffc2b3399d2d3f160d56385a4c9a3f56f","tid":416391,"uid":38316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T03:39:37.000Z","msg":"老實講歐洲個工時又係過份啲既<br />\n我覺得你搵英國或者美國比合理啲<br />\n<br />\n除非你做到好似德國咁準時有效率<br />\n唔係最後都係變晒歐豬"},{"pid":"10adef454b166f04f5f0e9f235b0779330725132","tid":416391,"uid":38316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T03:42:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>歐洲人使唔使煩買樓？真心唔知</blockquote><br />\n人哋大多數石建築<br />\n唔會好似香港咁幾五六十年拆一次<br />\n啲樓動不動就一兩百年<br />\n以前我住個古Town起咗成五六百年添<br />\n<br />\n無嘜起樓既成本相對低好多<br />\n所以唔貴<br />\n<br />\n加埋地方大"},{"pid":"f1c442e450aeebd82ea5732bc1c185d54d9b1f82","tid":416391,"uid":111934,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T03:52:42.000Z","msg":"大家記唔記得97前一般白領係返朝九晚五<br />\n之後爆金融風暴, 好多公司裁員<br />\n有啲公司就「要脅」員工唔裁員, 不過就要放遲一個鐘<br />\n當時所謂叫「共渡時艱」<br />\n咁梗係唔使講, 經濟好返都唔會返轉頭放五啦<br />\n白領都要放六, 連帶藍領工種都超長工時"},{"pid":"213e810e587d56a55d6b37ab57ced0e8ab44b1ae","tid":416391,"uid":113205,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T03:59:22.000Z","msg":"地球上我哋同黑人跟本就係低等民族<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}